{"tid":254640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"瞓左無睇, 中國棋王柯潔大炒阿法狗幾多?","createTime":"2017-05-23T10:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T10:46:10.000Z","uid":106858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"752fceb940f27858cb80f17d5d4d07276304e373","tid":254640,"uid":106858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:37:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170523&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56727093&amp;ref=tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170523%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56727093%26ref%3Dtw&d=J1uo%2FmO6VmPpH2nce9jFjcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=1f4ce89d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170523%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56727093%26ref%3Dtw&h=0117807d\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170523&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56727093&amp;ref=tw</a><br />\n全球矚目的新一輪人機圍棋大戰今日展開，世界排名第一的19歲中國棋王柯潔，將與去年擊敗南韓棋王李世乭，並在今年初以Master身份在網絡上取得60連勝記錄的AlphaGo對弈，開賽時間為今早10:30，柯潔與AlphaGo將進行三番棋（三盤兩勝）對決。本報亦會緊貼人機大戰戰況，為讀者實時報道。柯潔在賽前最後一次接受內地媒體專訪談到致勝機會率，柯潔說：「會拼死一搏」。<br />\n<br />\n5月23日<br />\n<br />\n15:00 AlphaGo開發者DeepMind創辦人Demis Hassabis在Twitter留言：AlphaGo贏得首場勝利！柯潔戰得勇敢，有幾次下得相當好。（AlphaGo wins game 1! Ke Jie fought bravely and some wonderful moves were played.）<br />\n<br />\n14:58<br />\nAlphaGo執白1/4子戰勝柯潔，暫時以1比0領先。雙方的第二局比賽將於周四上午10時30分繼續進行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8c586f9026e3ee4cf4988940c130024b3d0472","tid":254640,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:41:45.000Z","msg":"alpha go都冇愛嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c306a7d10e5cac1e57f65ed6f448a0ce69ac45","tid":254640,"uid":106858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:46:10.000Z","msg":"佢之前唔係咗串我都唔會笑佢"}]}